AvaSoft 8.3.1

Release Date (yyyy-mm-dd): 2015-10-08

Changes / New features:

- Added PWM feature for the AvaSpec EVO
- Added 'Set All' buttons for setting 'Integration Time' and 'Number of Averages' in the spectrometer window.

Bug fixes:

- Fixed installer problem with plug-in applications in version 8.3.0
- Saving to ASCII in equidistant mode did not work in the 'Scope minus Dark' mode.
- Calculating board temperature was fixed for the AvaSpec Mini and EVO models.
   

